A '''copper rock''' is a rock that contains [[copper ore]]. It can be mined with a [[Mining]] level of 1. It is one of the first rocks that can be mined, along with [[tin rock]]s. Each time a player successfully mines a copper rock they gain 17.5 Mining [[experience]]. Mining 14 [[tin ore]] and 14 copper ore (wielding the pickaxe as a [[weapon]] to free the 28th [[inventory]] space) and smelting them to [[bronze bar]]s is a slow but effective way to train Mining and [[Smithing]].

For [[members]], it is not really known that players can [[power level]] the [[Mining]] skill with copper ore in the [[Port Khazard mine]] and amass ore. This is because of two fast [[respawn]]ing copper rocks that are very close to a [[bank deposit box]]. These two copper rocks are the closest mining rocks to a fast [[bank]] source, which surpasses the [[West Falador mine]] and level 5 [[Agility]] [[shortcut]].

On the other hand, [[free players]] can best gather their ores at [[East Varrock Mine]] and banking at [[Varrock East Bank]]. There is an [[aggressive]] level 6 [[giant rat]] for players under 13 [[combat level|combat]] en route to the bank, however.

